dispensary.name: Lionheart Cannabis - Helena
dispensary.description:
Lionheart Cannabis is Montana's premier cannabis dispensary, dedicated to providing the best strains and quality products to both medical and recreational customers. 

Lionheart has dispensaries in Billings, Butte, Bozeman. Four Corners, Great Falls, Helena, Kalispell, and Missoula. Be sure to visit and join our Rewards Program and get points you can spend like cash in any Lionheart dispensary.

products.name: Super Glue - Lionheart Cannabis
products.strainDescription: Superglue, also known as "Tacky Glue," is an indica-leaning hybrid strain that produces a functional and relaxing high to the mind and body. Smelling of pine and a sweet caramel aroma, this strain is bred by Seedism Seeds. Superglue is made by crossing Afghani and Northern Light. Those who enjoy Superglue say it relaxes you while still leaving you functional and energetic enough for social activities or even a productive afternoon.

products.name: Samoas
products.strainDescription: A cross between Forum Cut GSC and Face Off OG Bx1, Samoas—like the trademarked cookie—is here to level up the beloved GSC strain. Another strain from Archive Seed Back, this strain brings potency and flavor with big yields, and consumers and growers alike can expect an extra skunky Kush funk alongside the smooth delicious cookie terpenes we have grown to love.

products.name: Citrus Rush - Shake - Lionheart Cannabis
products.strainDescription: A collaboration between Archive Seed Bank and ORGNKID, Citrus Rush is a cross between Skunk Tangerine and Do-Si-Dos that produces frosty, potent buds. Balancing the dominant flavors of the two strains, Citrus Rush’s flavor profile is smooth like ice cream. This strain offers a powerful high that can be invigorating in small doses, but is more sedative in large quantities.

products.name: Menage - Shake
products.description: Embark on a thrilling journey with Menage by Lionheart Cannabis, a carefully curated blend of three exceptional strains. This hybrid masterpiece offers a harmonious balance, delivering a symphony of flavors and effects. Let the aromatic dance of Menage enchant your senses, leading you into a world of relaxation and euphoria. Elevate your cannabis experience with this captivating and versatile strain.
products.strainDescription: Menage is a weed strain that crosses (Zkittlez x Triangle Kush Bx3) x (Gelato #41 x Kush Mints #11). Menage has pungent minty, dessert, and OG Kush aromas and a hybrid indica effect. The modern strain is high in THC and great for after-work relaxation.

products.name: Ghost Train Haze - Lionheart Cannabis
products.description: Embark on a journey through the clouds with Ghost Train Haze, an electrifying strain available at Lionheart Cannabis! This sativa-dominant hybrid packs a powerful punch, featuring potent THC levels that can elevate your senses to new heights. Feel the euphoric rush and creative sparks as the Haze takes you on a spirited ride. The citrus and floral notes add a burst of freshness to the experience, leaving you with a memorable and uplifting high. Discover the thrill of Ghost Train Haze at Lionheart Cannabis and let your imagination soar!
products.strainDescription: First bred by Rare Dankness, Ghost Train Haze is a sativa cross of Ghost OG and Neville’s Wreck. Unlike typical sativas, Ghost Train Haze grows dense buds blanketed in white, crystal-capped trichomes. With a sour citrus and floral aroma, Ghost Train Haze delivers a potent dose of THC to knock out pain, depression, and appetite loss, but patients prone to anxiety should steer clear of this heavy-hitter. Low doses are conducive to concentration and creativity, but you may notice some cerebral haziness as you smoke more.

products.name: Dolato
products.description:
Embark on a sensory voyage with Dolato, a premium strain now gracing the shelves of Lionheart Cannabis!  Dolato, born from the union of Do-Si-Dos and Gelato, is a harmonious blend of Indica-dominance that promises an unparalleled experience for cannabis enthusiasts.

Indulge in the mesmerizing aroma of Dolato, where sweet berry notes dance alongside earthy undertones, creating an olfactory symphony. The visual allure is undeniable, with resin-coated buds boasting a captivating display of deep greens and vibrant purples.

Dolato's effects are a testament to its pedigree, offering a euphoric uplift that gracefully transitions into a relaxing body high. Whether you're seeking a moment of tranquility or a burst of creative inspiration, Dolato invites you to savor the richness of its terpene profile and the depth of its effects.

Elevate your cannabis journey with Dolato, an exquisite strain curated for discerning palates, now available at Lionheart Cannabis.
products.strainDescription: Dolato, also known as "Do-Si-Lato" and "Dosi-Lato," is an indica marijuana strain made by crossing Do-Si-Dos with Gelato #41. Dolato has a beautiful range of colors in its colas—from light to dark green and red-wine purple to bright orange, all dusted with diamond-like trichomes. Dolato’s terpene profile features a fruity, earthy scent followed by a sweet lavender taste. Dolato may leave people feeling stress-free and sedated, making it perfect for a slowed-down night in, perhaps paired with a bath and a book.

products.name: MAC1 - Montanabis
products.description:
Unveil the extraordinary with MAC1, a premium strain by Montanabis, now available at Lionheart Cannabis!  MAC1, short for Miracle Alien Cookies, is a hybrid masterpiece that captivates the senses from the first glance. Drenched in trichomes and bursting with vibrant hues, its buds are a testament to the strain's exceptional genetics.

Indulge in the symphony of flavors as MAC1 offers a complex profile that blends sweet citrus with hints of spice and earthiness. The effects are equally enchanting, delivering a euphoric uplift that gradually transitions into a state of deep relaxation. Whether you're a seasoned connoisseur or a curious explorer, MAC1 promises a journey through the cosmos of cannabis sophistication.

Elevate your experience and embrace the extraordinary with MAC1, exclusively curated by Montanabis and available at Lionheart Cannabis.

products.name: Cherry Punch #4
products.description: Indulge in the sweet embrace of Cherry Punch #4, a tantalizing strain awaiting your discovery at Lionheart Cannabis! This hybrid marvel seamlessly blends the luscious sweetness of ripe cherries with a punch of earthy undertones, creating an enchanting symphony of flavors. The effects are just as delightful, offering a balanced experience that eases the mind and relaxes the body. Cherry Punch #4 is your invitation to a flavorful journey where every inhale is a burst of fruity bliss. Elevate your senses and savor the magic of Cherry Punch #4, exclusively at Lionheart Cannabis.
products.strainDescription: Cherry Punch is a potent sativa-hybrid marijuana strain crossed between Cherry AK-47 and Purple Punch F2. Bred by Symbiotic Genetics, Cherry Punch (also known as Black Cherry Punch) is widely celebrated for its bold cherry flavor profile that comes from dense, citrus terpenes. Consumers who smoke this strain say it smells fruity and rich and a little skunk-like. The high you get from smoking Cherry Punch is uplifting and relaxing - perfect for jamming out to a new album or even taking care of a few errands. This strain is ideal for those seeking relief from anxiety and stress. Cherry Punch buds come in a dark green color with purple specks and striking orange hairs.

products.name: Mandarin Sunset
products.description: Embrace the warm embrace of Mandarin Sunset, a captivating strain waiting for you at Lionheart Cannabis! This indica-leaning hybrid boasts a delightful combination of citrus and earthy flavors, creating a symphony of taste with each inhale. Let the soothing effects wash over you, as the stress of the day melts away. Whether you're winding down or seeking a moment of tranquility, Mandarin Sunset invites you to savor the sunset of your day. Discover the magic at Lionheart Cannabis and unwind with the serene allure of Mandarin Sunset.
products.strainDescription: Bred by Ethos Genetics, Mandarin Sunset crosses Herijuana with Orange Skunk, creating an indica with a rich, skunky, orange flavor profile. If you find Mandarin Sunset in concentrate form be sure to give it a try, as its terpene profile has won numerous cups.

products.name: Pineapple Jaeger - Lionheart Cannabis
products.description: Immerse yourself in the tropical bliss of Pineapple Jaeger, a tantalizing strain available at Lionheart Cannabis! Experience the synergy of earthy undertones and sweet pineapple aromas that transport you to a sunny paradise. This hybrid strain offers a perfect balance, delivering a euphoric and uplifting high that soothes the mind and invigorates the senses. Let Pineapple Jaeger be your passport to a vibrant and elevated experience. Visit Lionheart Cannabis and savor the essence of this exceptional strain!
products.strainDescription: Jager, also known as "Jagermeister," "Jager Kush," and "JGR" is an indica marijuana strain made by crossing LA Confidential and Blue Dream. This strain produces full-body effects that are relaxing but not sedating. Jager tastes and smells like black licorice. This strain was named after the dark acloholic beverage from Germany. Jager is best enjoyed during the evening hours.

products.name: Blue Dream - Lionheart Cannabis
products.description:
Embark on a journey through the clouds with Lionheart Cannabis's iconic Blue Dream strain. A beloved hybrid that has captivated cannabis enthusiasts worldwide, Blue Dream is a testament to the artistry of Lionheart's cultivation. A harmonious blend of Blueberry and Haze genetics, this strain delivers an unparalleled experience that transcends the ordinary.

Behold the mesmerizing buds, adorned in a tapestry of greens and blues, generously sprinkled with a crystalline layer of trichomes. The aroma is a symphony of sweet blueberries underscored by subtle earthy notes, inviting you to explore the depths of its complex terpene profile.

As you indulge in Blue Dream, anticipate a gentle uplift that gracefully transitions into a blissful, euphoric state. This balanced hybrid is renowned for its ability to inspire creativity while maintaining a soothing sense of relaxation. The cerebral journey is complemented by a gentle body high, making Blue Dream a versatile companion for various occasions.

Lionheart Cannabis takes pride in curating a strain that embodies the essence of the Montana spirit. Whether you're a seasoned enthusiast or a curious newcomer, let Blue Dream be your passport to a world of elevated experiences. Elevate your senses, chase your dreams, and discover the magic of Blue Dream by Lionheart Cannabis.
products.strainDescription: Blue Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Blueberry with Haze. This strain produces a balanced high, along with effects such as cerebral stimulation and full-body relaxation. Blue dream is 18% THC but has a low CBD percentage, making this potent strain a fan favorite of both novice and veteran cannabis consumers. In terms of flavor, Blue Dream is reported to smell and taste like sweet berries. Medical marijuana patients often use Blue Dream to treat symptoms of depression, chronic pain, and nausea. Blue Dream originated in California and has since achieved legendary status among West Coast strains and has quickly become one of the most-searched-for strains in the Leafly database. The average price per gram of Blue Dream is $20. Strains similar to Blue Dream include Blue Dream CBD, Double Dream, and Blue Magoo.

products.name: Point Break - Marimint
products.strainDescription: Point Break is a strain worthy of a Keanu Reeves cameo—High Times deemed it a Strain of the Day for 4/20 week 2023. This hybrid from Surfr Seeds thrills with magenta, trichome-slick buds and fills the nose with the paradisal terps of its Tropicana Cookies (Mtn Cut) x Trophy Wife parents. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Point Break, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products.name: Menage - Empathy Cannabis
products.description:
Indulge your senses with Menage, a captivating strain from Empathy Cannabis, proudly featured at Lionheart Cannabis. This unique blend brings together three distinguished strains, creating a harmonious dance of flavors and effects.

Menage's buds boast a mesmerizing appearance, adorned with vibrant hues and glistening trichomes. As you explore its aromatic bouquet, notes of earthy pine, sweet citrus, and a hint of floral spice unfold, setting the stage for an enthralling experience.

This carefully curated combination of strains results in a symphony of effects that cater to both body and mind. Menage offers a balanced journey, starting with a euphoric lift that gradually transforms into a soothing body relaxation. It's the perfect choice for those seeking a versatile and pleasurable cannabis encounter.

Discover the allure of Menage by Empathy Cannabis, a sensory masterpiece awaiting your exploration at Lionheart Cannabis. Elevate your cannabis experience with this enchanting blend that promises a truly unforgettable ride.

products.strainDescription: Kush Mints is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Animal Mints and Bubba Kush. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. Kush Mints is a potent and flavorful strain that has a minty and cookie-like aroma and flavor, with hints of gas and pine. It has a balanced high that is both relaxing and euphoric, with a pleasant body buzz and a creative mind. Kush Mints is 28% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Kush Mints effects include feeling relaxed, euphoric, and aroused. Medical marijuana patients often choose Kush Mints when dealing with symptoms associated with anxiety, stress, and depression. Bred by Mr. Nice Seeds, Kush Mints features flavors like mint, menthol, and pine. The dominant terpene of this strain is limonene. The average price of Kush Mints typically ranges from $15-$20 per gram. Kush Mints is a rare and exclusive strain that is not widely available, so if you find it at your local dispensary, don’t hesitate to try it out. Popular with medicinal growers, Kandy Kush provides a potent body high with pronounced pain relief.
